{"artist":null,"title":"The Book Of Heads","resource_url":"https://api.discogs.com/releases/920084","year":"1995","notes":"Recorded March 19, 1995 at Shelly Palmer Studio, NYC.\r\nMastered at Foothill Digital.\r\n\r\nOn Étude #8, Ribot plays a six-note melody while dragging a violin bow across the strings. \r\nOn #14, he plays a few random notes for thirty seconds. \r\nOn #16, he knocks on the body and plays a few bent notes. \r\nOn #21, he sounds like he's pulling the guitar apart, string by string. \r\nOn #23, the acoustic guitar becomes electric — and it sounds like a power drill. \r\n(The drill sound returns on #27, a very violent track.) \r\nOn #32, he plays different musical styles — funk, surf, and rock and roll.\r\n","uri":"https://www.discogs.com/John-Zorn-Featuring-Marc-Ribot-The-Book-Of-Heads/release/920084","images":[{"uri150":"https://img.discogs.com/hcCLbWiCBEdqlG_DHtZ7DXHCb-w=/fit-in/150x150/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(40)/discogs-images/R-920084-1173273564.jpeg.jpg","height":482,"width":499,"type":"primary"},{"uri150":"https://img.discogs.com/RkQVAogLb5B8iGrgk72B_YLNDVc=/fit-in/150x150/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(40)/discogs-images/R-920084-1548583895-3501.jpeg.jpg","height":590,"width":600,"type":"secondary"},{"uri150":"https://img.discogs.com/3TLAfCEVKzgIXRRso3NNwGIpaew=/fit-in/150x150/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(40)/discogs-images/R-920084-1548583901-5546.jpeg.jpg","height":592,"width":600,"type":"secondary"},{"uri150":"https://img.discogs.com/kbsV2VJ1g1GwBgPXxvWwdyX-FWQ=/fit-in/150x150/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(40)/discogs-images/R-920084-1548583912-8454.jpeg.jpg","height":603,"width":600,"type":"secondary"},{"uri150":"https://img.discogs.com/7ikXk0aruMiLT77PVLdX4IFXqfk=/fit-in/150x150/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(40)/discogs-images/R-920084-1548583928-7232.jpeg.jpg","height":617,"width":600,"type":"secondary"},{"uri150":"https